  "birth_place": "Upper Norwood",
  "description": "English philosopher (1873–1958)",
  "bio": "喬治·愛德華·摩爾，OM（George Edward Moore或G. E. Moore，1873年11月4日—1958年10月24日），英國哲學家，與伯特蘭·羅素一同被認為是分析哲學的主要創始人，主要貢獻為後設倫理學，知名作品有《倫理學原理》。\n摩爾認為和倫理相關的概念不可能用自然概念（例如：生存，功利，等）來解釋。",
  "bio_source": "zhwiki",
  "description_en": "English philosopher (1873–1958)",
  "bio_en": "George Edward Moore (4 November 1873 – 24 October 1958) was an English philosopher who, alongside Bertrand Russell, Ludwig Wittgenstein and earlier Gottlob Frege, was an initiator of analytic philosophy. He and Russell began de-emphasising the idealism which was then prevalent among British philosophers and became known for advocating common-sense concepts and contributing to ethics, epistemology and metaphysics. He was said to have had an \"exceptional personality and moral character\".",
  "bio_en_source": "enwiki"
}